Renée Taylor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ren%C3%A9e_Taylor 0 Renée Taylor (née Renée Wexler; March 19, 1933) is an American actress and writer. She is known for playing Fran Drescher's title character's outspoken mother, Sylvia Fine, on the TV series The Nanny.
